{
  "text": "Why is this trance state, as we call it, different? Why are there not protective entities available in this particular state? I am Ra. The uniqueness of this situation is not the lack of friends, for this, as all entities, has its guides or angelic presences and, due to polarization, teachers and friends also. The unique characteristic of the workings which the social memory complex Ra and your group have begun is the intent to serve others with the highest attempt at near purity which we as comrades may achieve. This has alerted a much more determined friend of negative polarity which is interested in removing this particular opportunity. We may say once again two notes: Firstly, we searched long to find an appropriate channel or instrument and an appropriate support group. If this opportunity is ended we shall be grateful for that which has been done, but the possibility/probability vortices indicating the location of this configuration again are slight. Secondly, we thank you for we know what you sacrifice in order to do that which you as a group wish to do. We will not deplete this instrument insofar as we are able. We have attempted to speak of how the instrument may deplete itself through too great a dedication to the working. All these things and all else we have said has been heard. We are thankful. In the present situation we express thanks to the entities who call themselves Latwii.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Why is this trance state, as we call it, different?",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 51,
        "start": 1.5,
        "end": 6.44
      },
      {
        "segment": "Why are there not protective entities available in this particular state?",
        "start_offset": 52,
        "end_offset": 125,
        "start": 7.44,
        "end": 22.48
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 126,
        "end_offset": 134,
        "start": 22.6,
        "end": 25.84
      },
      {
        "segment": "The uniqueness of this situation is not the lack of friends, for this, as all entities, has its guides or angelic presences and, due to polarization, teachers and friends also.",
        "start_offset": 135,
        "end_offset": 311,
        "start": 25.98,
        "end": 79.461
      },
      {
        "segment": "The unique characteristic of the workings which the social memory complex Ra and your group have begun is the intent to serve others with the highest attempt at near purity which we as comrades may achieve.",
        "start_offset": 312,
        "end_offset": 518,
        "start": 82.181,
        "end": 158.442
      },
      {
        "segment": "This has alerted a much more determined friend of negative polarity which is interested in removing this particular opportunity.",
        "start_offset": 519,
        "end_offset": 647,
        "start": 161.742,
        "end": 204.403
      },
      {
        "segment": "We may say once again two notes: Firstly, we searched long to find an appropriate channel or instrument and an appropriate support group.",
        "start_offset": 648,
        "end_offset": 785,
        "start": 208.143,
        "end": 253.843
      },
      {
        "segment": "If this opportunity is ended we shall be grateful for that which has been done, but the possibility/probability vortices indicating the location of this configuration again are slight.",
        "start_offset": 786,
        "end_offset": 970,
        "start": 255.903,
        "end": 321.964
      },
      {
        "segment": "Secondly, we thank you for we know what you sacrifice in order to do that which you as a group wish to do.",
        "start_offset": 971,
        "end_offset": 1077,
        "start": 324.404,
        "end": 364.565
      },
      {
        "segment": "We will not deplete this instrument insofar as we are able.",
        "start_offset": 1078,
        "end_offset": 1137,
        "start": 368.125,
        "end": 387.025
      },
      {
        "segment": "We have attempted to speak of how the instrument may deplete itself through too great a dedication to the working.",
        "start_offset": 1138,
        "end_offset": 1252,
        "start": 388.845,
        "end": 424.726
      },
      {
        "segment": "All these things and all else we have said has been heard.",
        "start_offset": 1253,
        "end_offset": 1311,
        "start": 426.326,
        "end": 443.266
      },
      {
        "segment": "We are thankful.",
        "start_offset": 1312,
        "end_offset": 1328,
        "start": 445.226,
        "end": 448.946
      },
      {
        "segment": "In the present situation we express thanks to the entities who call themselves Latwii.",
        "start_offset": 1329,
        "end_offset": 1415,
        "start": 451.246,
        "end": 480.526
      }
